Title: Simply breathing
Description: A Moment of Levity\\ We sailed for hours\ to each one's own\ A real firecracker, that one\ and others more somber\\ Did I mention the skies, so inviting that day\ with an effortless lift\ We could concentrate on things as important as\ simply breathing\\ A memory is in nature a dream\ of something we believe happened\ A moment cannot be charged with\ holding an entire afternoon\
